name: Grandmas House
description:
Go to your grandmas house, but don't eat to much!

This game was made for the Trijam #212!

You are at your grandmas house, and she gave you something to eat. But, don't eat too much, or too little. 

Try to get all the ending. There are three so good luck!

Thanks for playing this silly little game I made! Hope you had fun!

Made by Tak_Wacky
